sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Frontend (Next.js)
    participant A as ResumeAction
    participant G as GeminiAI
    participant P as PrismaDB
    participant R as Resume
    
    U->>F: Load Resume Builder
    F->>A: saveResume(content)
    A->>P: upsert Resume
    P-->>A: resume data
    A-->>F: success
    F-->>U: Update UI
    
    Note over U,A: Later...
    U->>F: Improve section with AI
    F->>A: improveWithAI(current, type)
    A->>G: generateAIResponse(prompt)
    G-->>A: improved text
    A-->>F: new content
    F-->>U: Show improved section
    
    alt Save changes
        U->>F: Save
        F->>A: saveResume(newContent)
        A->>P: update Resume
    end
